import React from "react";

export const ContactForm = ({
  name,
  setName,
  phone,
  setPhone,
  email,
  setEmail,
  handleSubmit,
}) => {
  return (
    <>
      <form onSubmit={handleSubmit}>
        <label>
          Name:
          <input type="text" value="name" />
        </label>
        <label>
          Phone:
          <input
            type="tel"
            value="phone"
            pattern="^(?:\+?(61))? ?(?:\((?=.*\)))?(0?[2-57-8])\)? ?(\d\d(?:[- ](?=\d{3})|(?!\d\d[- ]?\d[- ]))\d\d[- ]?\d[- ]?\d{3})$"
          />
        </label>
        <label>
          Email:
          <input type="email" value={email} />
        </label>
        <input type="submit"></input>
      </form>
    </>
  );
};
